title: COUNTER-STRIKE CARBON
description:
Hello gamers. This time I will present a new cs 1.6 which is called counter strike carbon . Compared to the rest of the kit, this kit brings some well-chosen skin, beautiful sounds, optimal map texture and a lot of complexity.

This game can be played in two ways: single player with boots or multiplayer on the online servers. At the internet you will find only Romanian servers that offer a player, low lag and much fun.

This game remains one of the most played kits and the fact that it brings new skins makes it more enjoyable. In the game you have two teams, many modes, many maps. If you become a true player on a server, you can get admin.
